These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. the turkish is between the person who's hobby is reading and the colombian##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the british##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the person eating corn##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, tennis
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person who's sport is basketball and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis | basketball | biathlon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

