.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the fan of gospel is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person driving the bus and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

