.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

