.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the librarian is between the person driving the boat and the dressmaker##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

