.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the fan of pop is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

