4. the designer is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | designer | police-officer | musician | nurse     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

