2. the spanish is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the italian##2
4. the owner of the rabbit is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian | egyptian | pakistani |
| Pet           | lizard  | rabbit  | goldfish | goat      |

