.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, singing, sudoku
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the owner of the cat and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing    | sudoku     | card-games | dancing |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

